title: Sean Conover Ad Day
description: DAKINE tags along with Sean Conover and the boys in North County SD. They start the day at Oceanside’s Melba Bishop skate park. Then Sean heads over to tangle with a sketchy run up and a wooden rail. After the dust settles, he ends up at Del Taco and gets a consolation prize for a hard days work.
